import { Grid, Typography } from "hero-design";

export default function DocumentOverView({doc}:{doc:any}) {
    console.log(doc)
    return (
        <Grid>
            <Grid.Row>
                <Grid.Col span={[12, 12, 12, 12, 12]}>
                    <Typography.Title>
                        Description
                    </Typography.Title>
                    <Typography.Text>
                        {doc.description}
                    </Typography.Text>
                </Grid.Col>
                <Grid.Col span={[12, 12, 12, 12, 12]}>
                    <Typography.Title style={{ textAlign:'center' }}>
                        Info 
                    </Typography.Title>
                </Grid.Col>
            </Grid.Row>
        </Grid>
    )
}
